Name: Greater Fenr Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Fenr Rune, Level 3 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes destruction and cataclysm, allowing those who channel it the ability to manifest aspects of the doom wolf.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACEThe Burning EndSPACEAs an action, you summon forth a fiery storm centered on yourself. All creatures of your choice within DISTANCE15-30DISTANCE feet of you must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes DAMAGE4-6DAMAGEd6 fire damage and is blinded for TIME1-3TIME turns, or half as much damage and is not blinded on a success.SPACESPACEYou may invoke this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 4 runic attunement slots. Requires Constitution 16 or greater to attune for a creature who did not craft the rune.
